comments: Batum (LAC) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) arm during his rip through as he starts his drive to the basket.
Jokic (DEN) makes marginal contact to Jackson's (LAC) body at the end of the drive.
Gordon (DEN) makes contact to Morris Sr.'s (LAC) body on the start of his drive that affects his SQBR.
Batum (LAC) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during the drive.
Morris Sr. (LAC) swipes down and makes hand on ball contact to dislodge the ball away from Gordon (DEN) on his shot near the rim.
Morris Sr. (LAC) moves forward and initiates contact to Jokic's (DEN) front which affects his shot near the rim.
Jokic (DEN) engages with Batum (LAC) during the loose ball and the contact is marginal.
Jackson (LAC) puts his hand completely under the ball during his dribble.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) body during his post up.
Morris Sr. (LAC) makes marginal contact to Jokic's (DEN) side on his shot near the rim.
Jackson (LAC) legally contests Jokic's (DEN) jump shot attempt and marginal contact occurs after Jokic's momentum carries him forward.

Coffey (LAC) has his rebounding position already established in Gordon's (DEN) path as he secures the rebound and attempts the shot.  His momentum carries him forward into Coffey (LAC) as he secures the ball.
